You have to create same `xml` for other `RadioButton`.

If you want to change the text color for selected `RadioButton` then here is xml. Put this xml file inside res&gt;color&gt;.

here is `radio_text_selector.xml` for text color.

    &lt;selector xmlns:android=&quot;http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android&quot;&gt;
        &lt;item android:state_pressed=&quot;true&quot; android:color=&quot;@color/colorPrimary&quot;/&gt;
        &lt;item android:state_checked=&quot;true&quot; android:color=&quot;@color/colorPrimary&quot;/&gt;
        &lt;item android:color=&quot;@color/dividerColor&quot;/&gt;
    &lt;/selector&gt;

